item.title: About
item.description: My name is Johny James. I am a software engineer searching for next moon shot. Interested in algorithms, linux, cli and many more. Follow me on twitter to get tech retweets. DMs are open. I work on some hobby projects duing my free time, which are hosted in github. I used to spend a lot of time on stack overflow answering on tags like regex python awk etc. Work these days prevent me from spending much time on the site.
